lt, just as he was required to give directions to a torture camp, because stupidity was the single abiding law of the universe.', 17777, 0), (356031, 'So this is what men are like. Well, that''s it, then - I am going to be a lesbian.', 2310, 0), (356032, 'Do not feel sorry for the bad luck of people, because behind everyone’s misery is their own stupidity and laziness.', 4238, 0), (356033, 'Stupidity of proving yourself when not required is itself a proof of stupidity.', 11145, 0), (356034, 'It''s not easy to kill a mountain goat. He thinks with his spine.', 2732, 0), (356035, 'No evidence is powerful enough to force acceptance of a conclusion that is emotionally distasteful.', 13409, 0), (356036, 'When stupidity knocks at the door, it is stupidity that opens it.', 6269, 0), (356037, 'Silly,'' he said with mock serenity, ''isn''t a word you should ever apply to people. They may be totally stupid, in fact, but if you call them silly you''ve lost their vote.', 2320, 0), (356038, 'Genuinity is mother of stupidity.', 11145, 0), (356039, 'Humanity is OK, but 99% of people are boring idiots.', 769, 0), (356040, 'There are so many different kinds of stupidity, and cleverness is one of the worst.', 778, 0), (356041, 'Actually, I was prone to random acts of stupidity. I considered it to be one of my talents.', 366, 0), (356042, 'The fourth approved approach for the problem of frontally attacking a guarded wormhole was to shoot the officer who suggested it.', 1690, 0), (356043, 'Fear is a communicable disease', 57323, 0), (356044, 'Listen, last time I talked to you three, you were all two oars short of having any oars, so I don''t want to hear it.', 6018, 0), (356045, 'Stupidity is doomed,therefore, to cringeat every syllableof wisdom.', 1083, 0), (356046, 'I didn’t say you weren’t smart. I said you were stupid.”“I guess I’m too dumb to see the difference.', 7713, 0), (356047, 'Most of your heritage comes from your culture, stupidity is one of them.', 4238, 0), (356048, 'I co